quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  56,77,"Toto eyo ni Ikurani yoluyali."
  56,78,"Mushitabu shialindwa."
  56,79,"Shashitilangakhwo tawe halali Omutswenufu."
  56,80,"Sheshibwa okhurula khu Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  56,81,"Ne kano namakhuwa kamulekanga?"
  56,82,"Amwakhopele orio khumukabo kwenyu (kwa abahele) nanyu mwikhola mbu muyingananga?"
  56,83,"Kaliba karie olwa omwoyo kuliuula khulukamukamu (mwikolomero)?"
  56,84,"Ne enywe ebise ebo muhenganga."
  56,85,"Ne efwe khuli ahambi muno ninanyu, nanyu shimukhulolanga tawe."
  56,86,"Ne enywe nikakhabanga mbu shimulirungwa tawe."
  56,87,"Kalusiekhwo omwoyo oko nikali mbu muboolanga obwatoto."
  56,88,"Ne naliba mubalia basutibwa hambi nende Nyasaye."
  56,89,"Kuliba omwikhoyo nende ebiokhuunya obulai, nende emikunda chomwikulu chobwokholo."
  56,90,"Ne naliba mubandu bomukhono omusatsa."
  56,91,"Ni omulembe khwiwe owuli Mubandu bomukhono musatsa."
  56,92,"Ne naliba Mubayingani Abakori."
  56,93,"Obucheni bwokhubukaniIwa bubwe buliba amaatsi kayile pa!"
  56,94,"Nende okhwinjisibwa mumulilo kwa Jahim."
  56,95,"Toto buno nibo obwatoto bwokhwisikwa."
  56,96,"Kho litswenule elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, Woluyali."
  57,1,"Bitswenulanga Nyasaye bili mwikulu nende mushialo, naye niye Owamaani, Owamachesi muno."
  57,2,"Nobubwe obwami bwo mwikulu nende khushialo. Niwelesinjia obulamu, khandi niye ufwisinjia, naye ni omunyali muno wa buli eshindu."
  57,3,"Ye niye wokhuranga na niye wokhumalilikha, naye niye owahabulafu nende owulalolekha, naye niye Omumanyi muno wabuli eshindu."